nodes.text: A male Human was a member of the Alliance to Restore the Republic during the Galactic Civil War. At some point he found himself cornered by three hostile armored beings - a Rodian, a Duros and a Human - and used his comlink to call for reinforcements.
This character was depicted on the "Reinforcements" card of the Champions of the Force, the base set of the Star Wars Galaxies Trading Card Game, which was illustrated by artist Darren Tan.
